@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Tabela de rutare (concept)

rectangle "Pachet primit\nDest = 10.20.0.5" as pkt
rectangle "Lookup in tabela" as lookup
rectangle "Decizie:\nnext hop / interfata" as decision

pkt --> lookup
lookup --> decision

note right of lookup
  Cautare pe baza:
  - prefix (longest prefix match)
  - metrica / cost
  - ruta implicita (0.0.0.0/0)
end note

note right of decision
  Rezultat:
  - trimite pe interfata X
  - sau catre next hop Y
  - sau drop (fara ruta)
end note
@enduml
